data.description: Nestled on a sprawling 5.68 acres, 4161 Lylewood Rd in Indian Mound, TN, offers a unique blend of tranquility and modern living. This charming property features a well-designed residence with 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a versatile office space.  Step into a spacious 1650 sqft home where every detail reflects a harmonious balance of comfort & style. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living spaces, providing a warm and inviting atmosphere. The two bedrooms offer a serene retreat, while the additional office space adds flexibility to suit your lifestyle needs.  Outside, the expansive 5.68 acres provide endless possibilities for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the beauty of nature. Whether you seek a peaceful haven or an ideal space for entertaining, this property offers a rare combination of space, privacy, and convenience.  Experience the best of rural living without compromising on modern comforts. Don't miss the chance to make 4161 Lylewood Rd your dream home.
